become a man?

34
00:03:03,633 --> 00:03:04,633
-Yeah, yeah.

35
00:03:04,733 --> 00:03:07,666
Can we go home and
get some food now?

36
00:03:07,766 --> 00:03:08,207
-Gotcha.

37
00:03:09,433 --> 00:03:10,366
-I knew it!

38
00:03:10,466 --> 00:03:12,166
I just knew you were
going to try that.

39
00:03:12,266 --> 00:03:13,966
-Look, a 100 yen piece.

40
00:03:14,066 --> 00:03:16,300
-Look, right in front
of you, a 500 yen piece.

41
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,533
-It must have fallen out of my--

42
00:03:18,633 --> 00:03:20,033
-Oh, like you really
have that much.

43
00:03:22,133 --> 00:03:23,633
-Think you can take me, huh?

44
00:03:23,733 --> 00:03:24,666
-You know it old man.

45
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:28,733
-Why you gotta be
so disrespectful?

46
00:03:28,833 --> 00:03:30,733
-Hey, you're the
one who started it.

47
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,100
-Oh.

48
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,866
[grunting]

49
00:03:39,966 --> 00:03:42,133
-Uh, Ranma, would you
mind moving from my seat?

50
00:03:43,566 --> 00:03:45,500
-Haven't you two been
fighting long enough?

51
