53
00:03:50,666 --> 00:03:51,966
-I what?!

54
00:03:52,066 --> 00:03:52,800
-I'm waiting.

55
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:53,966
WOMAN (OUTSIDE): Anyone home?

56
00:03:55,333 --> 00:03:55,866
KASUMI: Coming.

57
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,500
[growling]

58
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,166
-Mr. Saotome, you
have a visitor.

59
00:04:01,266 --> 00:04:02,166
-Who, me?

60
00:04:02,266 --> 00:04:03,933
-Knowing you, it's
a bill collector.

61
00:04:04,033 --> 00:04:05,666
-That would not surprise me.

62
00:04:05,766 --> 00:04:08,033
KASUMI: Actually, it's an
attractive older woman.

63
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,166
-Say it ain't so.

64
00:04:10,266 --> 00:04:11,700
There's got to be
some kind of mistake.

65
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,700
Right, Kasumi?

66
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,333
My old friend,
Saotome, the recipient

67
