69
00:04:17,566 --> 00:04:18,266
-Gee, Daddy.

70
00:04:18,366 --> 00:04:19,033
What's the matter?

71
00:04:19,133 --> 00:04:20,600
Are you jealous?

72
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:23,033
-Well, um, [clears throat],
um, you know.

73
00:04:31,433 --> 00:04:33,866
HAPPOSAI: What's with all
the bowing and scraping?

74
