-Why, you must be the
luckiest boy on Earth.

141
00:07:23,933 --> 00:07:25,466
-Hip hip hooray for me.

142
00:07:25,566 --> 00:07:26,400
-Oh, you cynic, you.

143
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:28,266
-Stop wasting time
and go straight

144
