RANMA: Akane, wait up!

146
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:34,900
Hey, I said wait up.

147
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,066
-Hey, Akane.

148
00:07:40,166 --> 00:07:41,133
There's a new
movie, just opened.

149
00:07:41,233 --> 00:07:42,166
Do you want to go see it?

150
00:07:44,266 --> 00:07:44,707
-Mm.

151
00:07:47,266 --> 00:07:47,707
-Huh?

152
00:07:49,766 --> 00:07:51,066
-Jeez, Akane.

153
00:07:51,166 --> 00:07:53,333
If that's how you're going to
be, next time I won't bother.

154
00:07:53,433 --> 00:07:55,033
-I know it's hard
on you right now,

155
00:07:55,133 --> 00:07:57,133
but don't you think
it might be smart

156
00:07:57,233 --> 00:07:59,066
for you to lie low for a while?

157
00:07:59,166 --> 00:08:01,866
-Why are you making such
a big deal out of this?

158
