TATEWAKI: I heard
the whole thing.

159
00:08:05,466 --> 00:08:08,333
If you think to escape the
rightful wrath of my most

160
00:08:08,433 --> 00:08:12,033
puissant self with your feeble
plots and schemes, think again.

161
00:08:12,133 --> 00:08:13,033
-I'm not trying to--

162
00:08:13,133 --> 00:08:14,733
-I don't care what
trouble you're in.

163
00:08:14,833 --> 00:08:16,633
You're not leaving until
we settle the score.

164
00:08:16,733 --> 00:08:17,700
You got that?

165
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,033
-Ryoga.

166
00:08:19,133 --> 00:08:21,600
MOUSSE: Yeah, who gave you
permission to go sneaking off?

167
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:25,600
-Listen up.

168
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,333
I don't know what's gotten
into you all of a sudden,

169
00:08:27,433 --> 00:08:29,433
but if you want
to fight, come on.

170
00:08:29,533 --> 00:08:30,800
KODACHI: Ranma, honey!

171
00:08:32,266 --> 00:08:33,966
-Ranma, honey, is it true?

172
00:08:34,066 --> 00:08:36,633
Are you really going away
to live with your mother?

173
00:08:36,733 --> 00:08:39,066
-Some day, she be
Shampoo mother too.

174
00:08:39,166 --> 00:08:40,900
Why you no introduce
so far, Ranma?

175
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,433
-I'm not in the mood for--

176
00:08:43,766 --> 00:08:46,800
-You know I'd follow you
anywhere, don't you darling?

177
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:47,333
-Come on.

178
00:08:47,433 --> 00:08:48,300
Let him go.

179
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,366
He's turning blue.

180
00:08:49,466 --> 00:08:51,466
-Silence, you insolent wench.

181
00:08:51,566 --> 00:08:53,400
What knowest you of a
woman's finer feelings?

182
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:54,333
-Plenty, you snob.

183
00:08:54,433 --> 00:08:55,633
-After all, he was
my fiance first.

184
00:08:55,733 --> 00:08:57,100
-What you talking?

185
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,500
He belong Shampoo
as much as you.

186
00:09:01,066 --> 00:09:01,933
-I can't breathe.

187
